    body: "## Clustered JMX via Management Center   &lt;font color=\&quot;#3981DB\&quot;&gt;**Hazelcast IMDG Enterprise**&lt;/font&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;   Clustered JMX via Management Center allows you to monitor clustered statistics of distributed objects from a JMX interface.   "
